Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the finale of this whole launch debacle of the Nvidia 50 series Blackwell cards. With the benchmarks now out, it's easy to see that the jump from generation to generation hasn't been anything to really write home about. AMD however is around the corner with the RX 9070 XT with a price you just can't beat. Thanks for watching!
